Alphagram is committed to creating a secure and private community for the most comprehensive social experience for Telegram users worldwide.

Alphagram is a third-party social app explicitly developed for Telegram users worldwide, produced by Telegram enthusiasts in Singapore, Taiwan, Hong Kong, and Cambodia. It is mainly built on top of the native Telegram infrastructure to provide more convenience and peace of mind with the following unique features.

►Incognito: Incognito mode, the other party can't see the message read double checkmark
►Translate: Instantly translate every message that needs to be translated
►Clear: Clear all unread messages with one click
►Grouping: Automatically group messages into categories
►Accounts: Expand support to 20 personal accounts
►Scan: Quickly scan the code to add friends
►Search: Quickly search for groups and channels you want to find
►Information: Dynamic wall-like interface to gather the content of your subscribed channels
►Themes: Personalized, exclusive 3D dynamic chat background themes
►Download: Easy and convenient download management, eliminating the hassle of large files filling up space

Alphagram is a third-party Telegram developer that continues the reliable and secure service of native Telegram in the essential experience and provides a more complete social and communication expertise with the basic needs of chat.

Infrastructure
►Sync: You can simultaneously log in and view social messages from all your phones, tablets, or any mobile device. No need to open backups or transfer chats between devices; type on any device and then continue to finish your messages on another device, and never lose your chat history again.

►Security: Our mission is to provide the best possible security and ease of use. Everything on Telegram TG, including chats, groups, media, and more, is encrypted using a combination of 256-bit symmetric AES encryption, 2048-bit RSA encryption, and Diffie-Hellman secure key exchange.

Social Features
►Fun: Telegram TG has powerful photo and video image editing tools, animated stickers and emojis, fully customizable themes to change the look and preferences of your app, and we offer a more open sticker/GIF platform for all your expressive needs, including the ability to create "My Favorites" to collect hundreds of graphic images.
►Private: We take your privacy seriously and will never give any third party access to your data. You can delete any message you send or receive for both parties and leave it clean.
►Secret: For those of you with a higher need for privacy, Alphagram offers a secret chat feature. In addition to encrypting your secret chat messages, they can be automatically self-destructed from the device you are chatting with. This way, you can send and disappear all types of content, including chat messages, photos, videos, and even files. Secret Chat uses peer-to-peer encryption to ensure that the intended recipient only reads messages.

100% free and unlimited

► Simplicity: While offering a fantastic set of new features, we took great care to keep the interface simple. Alphagram is so easy to use that we're sure you already know how to use it.

► No limits: You can send media and files without limitations on their type and size. Your entire chat history doesn't need to use storage space on your device, and even if you have a lot of temporary files, you can clear all the temporary space in the tool at any time with one click. It will be safely stored in Telegram's native cloud service for as long as needed.

Alphagram is the perfect tool for hosting online communities and teamwork.
►Open: Finally, Alphagram provides developers with a fully documented free API, open source app, and verifiable feature build to prove that the app you download is open-source software built from the same source code as the native version.
